  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "2. Roll out the pie crust and place it in a greased tart pan.",
    "3. In a bowl, whisk together the eggs, milk, Sterbottensost cheese, mild cheese, and mustardy cheese.",
    "4. Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "5. Pour the egg mixture into the pie crust.",
    "6. Bake for 35-40 minutes, or until the quiche is set and the crust is golden brown.",
    "7. Let it cool for a few minutes before serving."
